  (str content) (str `[Amendment of Act 27of 1962.] Rep. by the Repealing and Amending Act, 1974 (56 of 1974), s. 2
and the First Schedule (w.e.f. 20-12-1974).`)
  (str footnotes) (str )
  (str query) (str abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_20_00011_196861_1517807320262&sectionId=38997&sectionno=3&orderno=3&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_20_00011_196861_1517807320262)
